track.name: Little Acorns
comments: Fun fact: for a moment I thought I screwed up my media player and switched over the radio.  This song has been the intro to my absolute favorite radio show for years. I can't believe, I just found that out. Maybe they haven't hyped The White Stripes enough? Well, there are no excuses, I'm just totally ignorant, so what's the next song?  :)
These guys are way better than Nirvana, you lame band-wagoners!!! stop trying to compare pure Soul/Art with synthetic manufactured crap!
